headline: Eaton (ETN): Evaluating Valuation After Debut of 800 VDC AI Data Center Architecture
summary: Eaton, one of the leading power management companies, just unveiled a new reference architecture aimed at fast-tracking the use of 800 VDC power in artificial intelligence data centers.
